<br>
That said, I respect Starspun and have grouped with many members of your guild, BUT-- I have also been KSd, and most recently had a Starspun member ninja loot and greed up loot in my group, feigning igonorance because I didn't speak Elven well. It happens even with the best-- I've been in guilds on other servers where it took months before we figured out that a member had to go because he was a bad apple...<br>
<br>
My point is that I and others of the Oaken WERE concerned about this, and spoke in /gu chat about it. There are 2 sides to the story-- tempers were flared. I'm glad the issue was brought up to be addressed, but what followed was sad.  Before anything could be done, there were allegations questioning the honor of all members of the guild.  This forum was used not only to address a problem and get advice on it, but to name names and directly harm reputation. On other servers, maybe I wouldn't care about a rant on a message board-- FV is a differnt community though...<br>
<br>
oh well--- i'm done.<br>
<br>
Rumble<br>
